<GUIClass name="CMUI_YardAllocationControl" id="48260ed8-fc4d-4091-838e-cb72a5676603">
    <superclass name="BaseControl"/>
    <transient/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <access>protected</access>
    <text>This control consists of a Folder, with three Sheets, for Locations, Criteria and Options.

Locations Sheet layout:
+--------------------------------------------------------+
| Enter a location      XXXXXXXXXX&lt;TextBox&gt;XXXXXXXXXX    |
|                                                        |
|                       XX&lt;BtnAdd&gt;XX  XX&lt;BtnDelete&gt;XX    |
|                                                        |
| Locations Selected  +-----------------------------+    |
|                     |                             |    |
|                     |                             |    |
|                     |         &lt;Listbox&gt;           |    |
|                     |                             |    |
|                     |                             |    |
|                     +-----------------------------+    |
| Sort For:                                              |
| O In    O Out     XX&lt;BtnMoveUp&gt;XX  XX&lt;BtnMoveDown&gt;XX   |
|                                                        |
| Fill Option IN    XXX&lt;Combobox valid Options&gt;XXX       |
|                                                        |
| Fill Option OUT   XXX&lt;Combobox valid Options&gt;XXX       |
|                                                        |
|                      XX&lt;BtnSave&gt;XX  XX&lt;BtnCancel&gt;XX    |
+--------------------------------------------------------+

Criteria Sheet layout:
+--------------------------------------------------------+
| Criteria Attribute XXX&lt;Combobox of criteria types&gt;XXX  |--}
|                                                        |   }
| +-------------------+            +-------------------+ |    }
| |                   |  btnAdd    |                   | |     }
| |     list of       | btnAddAll  |     list of       | |      }
| |    available      | btnRemove  |     selected      | |       }
| |      codes        | btnRemAll  |      codes        | |        }
| |                   |            |                   | |         }
| +-------------------+            +-------------------+ |          } This itself is a common custom control.
|                              X&lt;BtnAdd&gt;X  X&lt;BtnDelete&gt;X |         }
| +----------------------------------------------------+ |        }
| | Voyage: V123, V124                                 | |       }
| | ISO-Type: 2040, 2038                               | |      }
| | IMEX: Export                                       | |     }
| |                                                    | |    }
| |                                                    | |   }
| +----------------------------------------------------+ |--}
| Code         XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX&lt;Textbox&gt;XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX |
| Description  XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX&lt;Textbox&gt;XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX |
| Remarks      +---------------------------------------+ |
|              |                                       | |
|              |            &lt;Large Textbox&gt;            | |
|              |                                       | |
|              +---------------------------------------+ |
|                                                        |
|                        XX&lt;BtnSave&gt;XX  XX&lt;BtnCancel&gt;XX  |
+--------------------------------------------------------+

Options Sheet layout:
+--------------------------------------------------------+
| +------------------------------------+                 |
| | Enquiry Type                       |                 |
| |    O Never                         |                 |
| |    O Voyage Departure              |                 |
| |    O When Empty                    |                 |
| |    O Specified Date  XX&lt;DateboxXX  |                 |
| +------------------------------------+                 |
|                                                        |
| Colour                XXXXXX&lt;TextBox&gt;XXXXXXX           |
| Allow Others          XXXXXX&lt;ComboBox&gt;XXXXXX           |
| If No Location Found  XXXXXX&lt;ComboBox&gt;XXXXXX           |
| Priority Adjustment   XXXXXX&lt;TextBox&gt;XXXXXXX           |
| Test Overstow Weight  XXXXXX&lt;CheckBox&gt;XXXXXX           |
|                                                        |
|                        XX&lt;BtnSave&gt;XX  XX&lt;BtnCancel&gt;XX  |
+--------------------------------------------------------+</text>
